title: Adventure Time Complete Season 1 2 3 4 5 720p - TinyMP4
description:
Adventure Time Complete Season 1 2 3 4 5 720p - TinyMP4

An attempt to bring excellent quality with smaller file sizes!

Video: MPEG4 x264
Audio: MPEG4 FAAC
Resolution: 1280x720

- All files are based on Web-DL for best quality and no Cartoon Network watermark.
- Files are about as small as they can be without a huge quality loss (+/- 5-10%).
- Intros and credits have been stripped from each episode but are included.
- Sizes vary: videos are encoded at a constant quality and not a constant size.
- Larger files do not mean better quality, it means more complex scenes.
- If you want the absolute best definitive quality, this torrent is not for you.

If you prefer the episodes in "Season" folders, rename file "#CreateFolders.txt" to
"#CreateFolders.bat". Copy to directory with episodes and run it. TPB wouldn't allow
batch files in the video category so I had to upload as a text file. Before doing
this, please make sure to seed for awhile!
